3.7 Statistical transformations

ggplot(data = diamonds) + 
  geom_bar(mapping = aes(x = cut))

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data = diamonds) + 
  stat_summary(
    mapping = aes(x = cut, y = depth),
    fun.ymin = min,
    fun.ymax = max,
    fun.y = median
  )
